    <data key="d0">Fortinet FortiWeb Cloud WAF as a Service Multi-Region Architecture</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Yju3yReAQtc</data>
    <data key="d2">Redesigned serverless management plane spanning multiple regions (US-WEST-1 and EU-CEN-1) to address data sovereignty, reduce egress costs, and keep security processing close to user applications.</data>
    <data key="d3">control, data_ingestion</data>
    <data key="d4">True</data>
